  "notes": [
    "Keys are Zepto's real taxonomy: '<category>::<subcategory>'. Use the exact strings returned by Zepto's product detail payload (case-sensitive).",
    "Most entries will be auto-generated by scripts/06a-bootstrap-baselines.ts using Gemini once the catalog is scraped. The hand-authored entries below are the curated anchors that override LLM guesses (priority=10).",
    "`nutrients` weights are signed and don't need to sum to 1 — they're rescaled at scoring time. Positive = higher is better, negative = higher is worse. Keys must match lib/supabase/types.ts::ProductNutrition.",
    "Bands encode how 'whole' the category is. A best-in-class chip should never beat an average paneer."
  ],
